Perfect! Your VisibleDx application is now running. The development server is active at **http://localhost:3000**.

The issue was that the development server wasn't running. It's now successfully started and ready for you to access your educational dermatology training tool with all the recent updates:

- ✅ Creator attribution (Willem Gielen MD)
- ✅ MIT License implementation  
- ✅ Dutch medical terminology fixes (SOEP)
- ✅ Vercel Analytics integration
- ✅ Enhanced multilingual support (EN/NL/DA)

You can now access your application at **localhost:3000** and continue working on those cool enhancement ideas we discussed!
